<br>
Ulvanth takes another long pull from his mug of ale<br>
<br>
Well then ther' be ye lass, talkin' aboot balance which be all good and well methinks.Yet I also be 'earin' ye say that ye will switch sides fight fer both good and evil to maintain this balance, and aye this also be soundin' good at times, yet t'nae be that simple. Ye must know when to fight with the good and when to fight with the evil. T'is nae always aboot keepin' the balance t'is mer impertantly aboot servin' justice, and while balance in the werld most often be what be just t'is nae alwqays the case, ye would do well to rememb'r that lass.<br>
<br>
